name: Libbpg for OS X
tagline: A stable version (0.9.5) of http://bellard.org/bpg/ which doesn't run into an segmentation fault 11 on OS X.
body:
### BPG Generator CLI
A stable build from source (v0.9.5) of the original BPG generator cli from http://bellard.org/bpg/. This build is for OS X and doesn't run into an segmentation fault 11.
